   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>As a temporary example, the latest addition to "Recent Activity" is "Greg
Grossmeier (greg) added an answer to the question “What's a good bug in Gwibber
for a newcomer to tackle?” · 7 minutes ago" but if I go to the Gwibber project
page, every Chatter answer is listed as having been submitted 7 hours ago,
including the highlighted newcomer question. I actually can't find a project
page that has more than one particular time amongst its Chatter answers.</pre>
